Sentencas: Yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) with 8 mol% Y was deposited by reactive magnetron sputtering onto oxidized (100) silicon substrates.
Titulo: Nanoporous YSZ film in electrolyte membrane of Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: It was possible to switch film texture from (111) to (200) by applying a strong RF substrate bias.
Titulo: Nanoporous YSZ film in electrolyte membrane of Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Transmission electron microscopy showed that the film deposited under bias is porous and exhibits nanoscaled grains.
Titulo: Nanoporous YSZ film in electrolyte membrane of Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: whereas the film deposited without bias is dense and columnar.
Titulo: Nanoporous YSZ film in electrolyte membrane of Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The ionic conductivity as a function of temperature revealed an activation energy of 1.04 eV.
Titulo: Nanoporous YSZ film in electrolyte membrane of Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The mechanical stress could be tuned to low values by thermal post-annealing.
Titulo: Nanoporous YSZ film in electrolyte membrane of Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Using the dense (111) film as electrolyte layer, and the porous (200) film as an interlayer to a porous Pt anode, an open circuit voltage of 0.85 V was obtained in a micro machined fuel cell structure.
Titulo: Nanoporous YSZ film in electrolyte membrane of Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell
